reviewText: Continuation of an excellent series, bringing the viewer closer to the characters and their daily problems and victories.
Loved this show. Was sad it was taken off the air.
glad it is out. only issueis that the music is distorted sometimes.
One of my all time favourite shows. This dvd collection is great. I'm very happy with both the content and quality of it.

I had purchased the first release of season 1 and had been waiting for the rest of the series to be offered.  While I am glad the rest of the series is finally available, the small print on the packaging states that some episodes have been edited and the music has been changed. I am really disappointed in the fact that it doesn't seem that these are the full original airings.
